<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Octopus on Mark Ridgwell | Notes</title><link>https://notes.markridgwell.com/tags/octopus/</link><description>Mark Ridgwell | Notes (Octopus)</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><lastBuildDate>Sun, 09 Apr 2023 17:20:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://notes.markridgwell.com/tags/octopus/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Octopus tentacle install arch</title><link>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/octopus/</link><pubDate>Sun, 09 Apr 2023 17:20:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://notes.markridgwell.com/posts/linux/octopus/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="installing-polling-octopus-tentacle-on-arch" >Installing polling octopus tentacle on arch
